  Locus:
    Page: 264
    Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Illusions
---
This waking life is just a long dream which keeps our attention away from
what we really are. If you take the attitude that all the happenings in
the world are dream events, your mind becomes tranquil. It is only when
you take the dream world to be real that you get agitated.
